    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> ground fennel seeds</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
