    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir through your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
