    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Grate any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
